  Source:
    Title: Young India
    Editor: M. K. Gandhi
    Locus:
      Date: 5 March 1925
---
He is a personal God to those who need His personal presence. He is embodied
to those who need His touch. He is the purest essence. He simply is to
those who have faith. He is all things to all men. He is in us and yet
above and beyond us.
